		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Uses hardest difficulty = LEVEL 8
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Player character : Wan Fu
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Purpose of this movie
		$LF
		[ol 
			[li 
				" Make audiences feel refreshed by beating all CPUs up with powerful attacks, with maximum power (to be at the maximum stat with below)
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" To show crazy moves, to attack enemies by "Exploding Confucious" which is not a popular to take a damage, basically at the end of the 1st round
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" To give an entertainment, e.g. Deformed Transformation -> quick counter, some glitches - to get Perfect even with not full HP at Hanzo or Mizuki stage, Unnatural combo at the end of Wan Fu stage (Confucious Slash can't make 3 combos usually), copy opponent's movement at Wanfu Stage, Wanfu is behind the pillar at the end of some stages even though he is laughing, etc.
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" With all of above, try to complete the game as quick as possible, try to beat all opponents before the time becomes below 80.
				$LF
			]li
		]ol
	]li
