[h3 id=Comments 
	" Comments
	$LF
]h3
[div class=p 
	"People loves Samurai Shodown series (Samurai Spirits) because players can beat their opponents with incredibly strong slashes when they are at the maximum power.
	$LF
	"I tried to get Perfect in all stages in Samurai Shodown 1 movie, however, it causes lack of excitement.
	$LF
	"Therefore, in this movie I tried to gain a maximum Power in every stages with the crazy special move, "Exploding Confucious", to hit player character's own head on the pillar. In order to avoid a big loss in-game, basically I used this one at the end of the 1st round. For some stages not.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Samurai Shodown 2 has more special moves so I didn't stick only to the finish move can damage the weapon (POWER SPECIAL: Wrath of God Blowout)
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Other characters like Haohmaru has more powerful moves e.g. Heaven Supreme Sealing God Slash, however, Wanfu doesn't have rushing combo, so I tried to be dynamic even though I couldn't show many hit combos.
	$LF
]div
